cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this component in your work, please cite using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "ferpa-haystack: FERPA-Compliant Document Filter for Haystack RAG Pipelines"
abstract: >
  Haystack-native document filter component enforcing FERPA access control
  at the retrieval layer. Implements two-layer identity-scoped filtering
  (student identity matching and category authorization) with automatic
  audit record generation per 34 CFR § 99.32. Prevents unauthorized
  education record disclosure before documents enter the LLM context window.
